# Canonicalise to the apex domain. Requires www.bushridingmap.com to be added
# as a custom domain on the Pages project so requests reach Pages.
https://www.bushridingmap.com/* https://bushridingmap.com/:splat 301!

# The map is now the homepage; keep old /map links (and deep links /map#id,
# whose hash the browser preserves) working.
/map / 301

# Static, server-rendered SEO route pages live under /routes/** (generated by
# `npm run build:seo`). Cloudflare Pages serves existing static files before it
# applies any redirect rule, so these are reached directly and must NOT be
# redirected. There is no SPA catch-all here, so nothing needs reordering — this
# note just documents that /routes/** is authoritative static content.
